    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Two of three QoIs (stiffness, yield force) satisfy the quantitative E/uval acceptance criterion with full uncertainty quantification. Force at 40 mm displacement passes the percent-difference acceptance bound; inherent variability in the post-yield regime was assessed qualitatively and judged acceptable for the Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence context. The single deficiency (Test conditions below required level) is acknowledged and does not preclude acceptance given the supporting evidence from the two fully characterized QoIs and the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol relative to in vivo loading.",
